has been in this building

00:50:25.810 --> 00:50:30.560
before, because he also did
a Google talk with the Black

00:50:30.560 --> 00:50:32.390
Google Live group.

00:50:32.390 --> 00:50:33.190
JULIE: BGN, yeah.

00:50:33.190 --> 00:50:34.490
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:50:34.490 --> 00:50:38.240
And so that shows
you that that kind

00:50:38.240 --> 00:50:44.600
of accessing the different
groups within the theater

00:50:44.600 --> 00:50:48.980
is an active thing
that's happening.

00:50:48.980 --> 00:50:50.480
But I think you're
absolutely right.

00:50:50.480 --> 00:50:52.940
That kind of solidarity
is really helpful.

00:50:52.940 --> 00:50:55.130
I think everybody
has their own agenda

00:50:55.130 --> 00:50:58.610
and their own unique
challenges, and that sometimes

00:50:58.610 --> 00:51:01.290
makes things difficult,
as you can imagine.

